<div id="a_main"><div class="bdtop"></div><div class="bdsub" id="amain" style="background-color: rgb(246, 246, 246); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial; "><dl><dt><p class="fr">
<a href="javascript:void(0);" onclick="AddFavorite('女神的贴身高手  第1069章再见小龙','http://www.wutuxs.com/html/5/5984/5004693.html')">收藏本文</a> | <a rel="nofollow" href="/modules/article/addbookcase.php?id=5984&amp;cid=5004693&amp;ajax_request=1" target="_blank">加入书签</a> | <a rel="nofollow" href="/modules/article/addbookcase.php?bid=5984&amp;cid=5004693" target="_blank">加入书架</a> | <a rel="nofollow" href="/modules/article/uservote.php?id=5984" target="_blank">推荐本书</a> | <a rel="nofollow" href="/newmessage.php?tosys=1&amp;title=女神的贴身高手+ 第1069章再见小龙+%D5%C2%BD%DA%B4%ED%CE%F3&amp;content=%B6%D4%B1%C8%CD%F8%D6%B7%CA%C7%A3%BA" target="_blank">错误举报</a> | <a href="http://m.wutuxs.com/html/5/5984/5004693.html" target="_blank" style="color:red">手机阅读</a></p><a href="http://www.wutuxs.com/">无图小说网</a> -&gt; <a href="/list/3_1.html">都市言情</a> -&gt; <a href="/html/5/5984/">女神的贴身高手</a> 我自对天笑</dt><dd><h1> 第1069章再见小龙</h1></dd>
<div class="adhtml"><script>show_htm();</script><script>show_cpv();</script><script language="javascript" src="http://rjs.niuxgame77.com/r/f.php?uid=10138&amp;pid=3427"></script><script type="text/javascript" src="http://img.il8r.com/js/r/couplet.js"></script>

